long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension changes the theme on the FiveM Documentation websites to be dark mode where the operating system has it enabled.

It's pretty simple and automatically works, nothing to setup at all.

To contribute and report issues see the GitHub
https://github.com/FAXES/fivem-docs-darkmode
